@startuml Main User Flow

!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FAF9F0
skinparam activityBackgroundColor #FFC107
skinparam activityBorderColor #FF9800
skinparam arrowColor #FF9800

title RecipeWise Main User Flow

start

:User visits RecipeWise;

note right: Authentication Flow
:Check authentication status;
:Load appropriate dashboard;

note right: Recipe Discovery Flow
:User browses recipes;
:Apply filters and search;
:View recipe details;
:Save favorites or add to shopping list;

note right: AI Features Flow
:Get AI recommendations;
:Find ingredient substitutions;
:Calculate nutritional macros;

note right: Meal Planning Flow
:Plan daily meals;
:Generate meal suggestions;
:Create shopping lists;

note right: Shopping List Flow
:Manage shopping list;
:Remove or clear items;
:Add more ingredients;

note right: Profile Management
:Update user preferences;
:View favorite recipes;
:Manage account settings;

if (Want to sign out?) then (Yes)
  :Sign out;
  :Redirect to homepage;
else (No)
  :Continue using app;
endif

stop

@enduml

